<|startoftext|>Dish: tsr version of yummy cornbread with a cream gravy
Directions: preheat oven to 325 degrees c
line baking tray with wax paper and grease
combine all ingredients except cheese
toss thoroughly with wire strainer
make mixture 1 1 / 4 thick , 3 / 4 thick , or until you reach desired thickness , but do not overmix
put mixture in container with remaining ingredients
cover with wax paper and let stand at room temperature for 20 minutes
using the wax paper , shape into a disk and refrigerate well before turning out
this allows for easier handling and keeps the filling from drying
