<|startoftext|>Dish: tsr version of yummy macaroni salad
Directions: in a casserole , combine the lettuce , peas and bacon
in a jar combine the mustard , salt , and pepper , mix well
place the cheese into jar , place over lettuce mixture , and shake well
place the sliced radishes and sun dried tomatoes in top corner of jar , around the edge of jar
drizzle with oil
place jar in 325 degree oven for 45-60 minutes , or until the cheese has melted just a little bit so it will be quite sweet for a bit
let cool a little
then gently add the salt and pepper to taste
to assemble , divide macaroni between 4 bowls
spoon the salad around the top of each bowl', top it off with lettuce and then the bacon and salad, 'it makes enough for 4 hungry people , but i think it would suit them too'<|endof
